    "rich_text_zFXL6k": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_hAN8HA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h4>Our products operate seamlessly in the background, appearing only when needed. Recognizing that technology is a means, not an end, our true focus is improving human lives. We prioritize universal and inclusive design from the start, creating solutions that empower all users in their living spaces.<\/h4>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_hAN8HA"
      ],
      "custom_css": [
        "h4 {max-width: 800px; font-weight: 400;}",
        " {padding-bottom: 50px;}"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "text_alignment": "left"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_W9KLyX": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_jRJcVC": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "A note from our founder",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_D9ra86": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Lotus’ story starts with me - I was born with twisted knees. And over the years I've been on and off crutches.<\/p><p>One night I got into bed, having left the lights on. But I was too tired to get on my crutches, hobble ten feet, turn off the light, and hobble back to bed. So I slept with the lights on — the entire night.<\/p><p>I didn't sleep well, and woke up thinking - if an Apple engineer like me doesn't have smart home tech in their own home, who does?<\/p><p>So that's our mission now - to build tech usable by everyone, simply by <em>optimizing<\/em> for disability first.<\/p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_jRJcVC",
        "text_D9ra86"
